        <summary style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #ededed; cursor: pointer; letter-spacing: -0.3px; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
          Does body weight affect caffeine metabolism?
          <span style="color: #444; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 300; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 16px;">+</span>
